{"tid":1783050,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"內心暴力行為唔暴力算唔算精神病","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T04:41:57.000Z","uid":74858,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3a986d3b65b6c72a83a32ca8d0b6183396e30eb2","tid":1783050,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"利伸先我今世人都冇郁過手<br />\n事源上巴士，條隊打蛇餅咁排<br />\n我就跟住前面個人排<br />\n點知上巴士嗰刻有個臭閪話我冇排隊(但我有) <br />\n我話條隊咁排架喎，佢話我扮晒野，仲同司機話d人唔排隊呀<br />\n我把口話收皮啦八婆<br />\n<br />\n但其實成程巴士我谷撚到想拎舊磚扑佢後腦死佢咁<br />\n因為比人屈好嬲<br />\n當然我係乜撚都冇做過 原因係我唔想坐監<br />\n冷靜過後我喺度諗其實我呢個幻想係正常人都會有<br />\n定係我反應特別大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果唔正常我會都好想睇下心理學家"},{"pid":"fb3244d85e96693f807e10d4cb6ba9c605b15d1b","tid":1783050,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:02:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zrNpRn5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzrNpRn5.jpg&h=7453738e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Hhk89N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Hhk89N.jpg&h=e421777a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FPC5APO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFPC5APO.jpg&h=08184019&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"513755df865c86a1bd20c0b647200e02db0fce4e","tid":1783050,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:24:23.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d1e8843f299bc88611c17a4371d0b5e68828276f","tid":1783050,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-